WEBVTT

00:00:57.847 --> 00:01:02.706
Today, the company enjoys 500 stores
with 8,000 employees.

00:01:03.077 --> 00:01:05.077
But it wasn't always the case.

00:01:05.514 --> 00:01:06.783
Three years ago,

00:01:06.807 --> 00:01:09.267
the demand for his dumplings was soaring

00:01:09.291 --> 00:01:12.211
due to consumers' craving
for healthy food.

00:01:12.815 --> 00:01:16.179
But the strong growth
of online food delivery services

00:01:16.203 --> 00:01:19.633
had pulled the consumers away
from store visits,

00:01:19.657 --> 00:01:22.180
causing a huge concern for GÄo.

00:01:23.125 --> 00:01:25.482
If I were to advise GÄo back then,

00:01:25.506 --> 00:01:28.743
I would go directly
with the classical approach,

00:01:28.767 --> 00:01:30.482
hiring venture managers,